        innovative web development, software solutions,
        AI-powered applications and modern digital experiences.
    </p>

    <a href="#services" class="btn">Get Started</a>
</div>

<div class="hero-image">
    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1055/1055687.png" alt="Technology">
</div>

</section>

<!-- Services -->
<section id="services">

<h2 class="title">Our Services</h2>

<div class="services">

<div class="card">
    <h3>Web Development</h3>
    <p>Create responsive and attractive websites for businesses and startups.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Software Development</h3>
    <p>Custom software solutions designed to improve productivity and efficiency.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>AI Solutions</h3>
    <p>Smart AI-based applications for automation and decision-making.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

